    {
      "id": "j401-h2-anchors",
      "type": "MARKDOWN",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "## 1. Cell Anchors — Naming Your Cells\n\nAdd `//@ anchor: name` as the first line of any code cell to give it a **stable, semantic name**.\nAnchors make cells reusable and referenceable by other cells and pipelines.\n\n```\n//@ anchor: math-utils\n//@ description: Core math functions\n```\n\nThe buttons **▶ With Deps** and **Run Pipeline** use these names to build the execution graph.",
      "output": "",
      "returnValue": null,
      "executed": false,
      "executionCount": null,
      "error": "",
      "anchor": null,
      "dependsOn": [],
      "pipelineSteps": []
    },
    {
      "id": "j401-imports",
      "type": "CODE",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "//@ anchor: imports\n//@ description: Common imports for the 401 notebook\nimport java.util.*;\nimport java.util.stream.*;\nimport java.util.function.*;\nimport java.time.*;\nSystem.out.println(\"[imports] Ready\");",
      "output": "[imports] Ready\r\n",
      "returnValue": "",
