      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "---\n\n## Summary\n\nYou've learned Venus Notebooks' full orchestration system:\n\n| Concept | Syntax | Purpose |\n|---------|--------|---------|\n| **Anchor** | `//@ anchor: name` | Name a cell for reuse |\n| **Depends** | `//@ depends: a, b` | Declare prerequisites |\n| **Namespace** | `//@ namespace: com.x.y` | Package scope for exports |\n| **Cross-notebook** | `//@ depends: notebook:id/anchor` | Import from any notebook |\n| **Pipeline** | `//@ steps: a, b, c` | Ordered workflow |\n| **MCP** | `GET /api/mcp/sse` | AI agent tool interface |\n\n### Quick Reference Card:\n```java\n//@ anchor: my-utils          ← names this cell\n//@ namespace: com.mine.utils  ← wraps as VNS_com_mine_utils when imported\n//@ depends: imports, base     ← runs these first (same notebook)\n//@ depends: notebook:java-101/methods  ← imports from another notebook\n//@ steps: load, transform, report      ← (PIPELINE cell only)\n//@ description: What this cell does    ← documentation\n//@ on-error: continue                  ← pipeline error handling (stop/continue)\n```",
